STM32CubeWBA
############

Origin:
   ST Microelectronics
   http://www.st.com/en/embedded-software/stm32cubewba.html

Status:
   version v1.9.0

Purpose:
   ST Microelectronics official MCU package for STM32WBA series.

Description:
   This package is an extract of official STM32CubeWBA package written by ST Microelectronics.
   It is composed of STM32Cube hardware abstraction layer (HAL) and low layer (LL) plus a set
   of CMSIS headers files, one for each SoC in STM32WBA series.

Dependencies:
    None.

URL:
   https://github.com/STMicroelectronics/STM32CubeWBA

Commit:
   92e834c2c34cf473b73271d54674a91a9c78477d

Maintained-by:
   External

License:
   BSD-3-Clause

License Link:
   https://opensource.org/licenses/BSD-3-Clause

Patch List:

   *Changes from official delivery:
    -dos2unix applied
    -trailing white spaces removed

   *Provision to enable hal & ll asserts added
    -Added stm32cube/stm32wbaxx/drivers/include/stm32_assert.h
    -Removed unused stm32cube/stm32wbaxx/drivers/include/stm32_assert_template.h

   *Fix to remove PAGESIZE definition which conflicts with POSIX
    Impacted files:
     drivers/include/Legacy/stm32_hal_legacy.h

   *Fix to remove XSPI HAL support as not present in WBAXX
    Impacted files:
     drivers/include/stm32wbaxx_hal_conf.h
     stm32cube/stm32wbaxx/CMakeLists.txt

   *Fix to encapsulate the header files of WWDG and TSC to avoid build errors
    due to missing definitions in the WBA2 SoC header files.
    Impacted files:
     drivers/include/stm32wbaxx_hal_tsc.h
     drivers/include/stm32wbaxx_hal_wwdg.h
   See release_note.html from STM32Cube
